{
  "stem": "3631.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In, in Germany, every year, the Nazi party had a, a party rally-- I think it was either in Munich or in Nuremberg-- where probably hundred thousands of Germans in, in their brown uniform, the brown shirts, assembled, and where they had hundreds of, of flags and the swastikas and the banners.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And of course, there was no television, but we saw it on radio, and we, we saw it all over.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, and Hitler would come and stand on top of these hundred thousands of people, and he would speak to them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and when he spoke, he, he was a very strong speaker.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He almost hypnotized the people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he, and he, he, he excited them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, and, and he, he instilled them with hatred, and, and with venom.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And, and to me, that was one of the most scary things to, to, to witness.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I always remember these big assemblies there, where, where the people stood, and they were screaming sieg hail and, and, and adoring this man.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And up to this day, when I hear any, any speaker who speaks with, with so much, with so much enthusiasm-- maybe that's the wrong word-- and so strongly with so much emotion, I get scared.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because if this is used in the wrong way, I think it's a very dangerous thing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I saw when I was in St.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Louis in a museum, a picture of one of these rallies they had there, and I was quite, quite touched by this picture, seeing this.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when we were picked up in, in, at the border, they said, where do you want to go?",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
